160
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:34,670
Thank you, Mother, for reminding me. I almost missed doing an important matter.

161
00:18:37,260 --> 00:18:39,210
- Slowly.
- Let go then.

162
00:18:39,210 --> 00:18:41,830
Come, slowly.

163
